# Search indexes — generated by `npm run gen:search`, which now runs on
# `prebuild`, so they're regenerated from committed content on every build.
# Never committed (build artifacts), so they can't go stale. (recordings-
# timings.json is NOT here — it needs the off-repo Whisper pipeline, so it stays
# committed.) A fresh clone needs one `npm run gen:search` for dev-server search.
/public/data/*-search*.json
